      "system": {
        "description": "<p>By uttering the phrase “Forget!” the user can make the Dominated victim forget the current moment as well as the last few minutes, enough to mask a superficial feeding or a chance meeting. No new memories are formed and if pressed the victim realizes they have a few minutes missing.</p><p>■ Cost: Free</p><p>■ Dice Pools: Charisma + Dominate vs Wits + Resolve</p><p>■ System: No roll is required against an unprepared mortal victim. Clouding the memory of a resisting victim or another vampire requires a Charisma + Dominate vs Wits + Resolve roll.</p><p>■ Duration: Indefinitely</p>",
