      "system": {
        "description": "<p>You rely on your stealth or Disciplines to feed from sleeping victims. If they never wake during the feeding, they won’t know you exist. Perhaps you were very anti-social in life; you don’t feel cut out for the intense interpersonal nightlife or physical violence of more extroverted hunters.</p><p>■ Add a specialty: Medicine (Anesthetics) or Stealth (Break-in)</p><p>■ Gain one dot of Auspex or Obfuscate</p><p>■ Gain one dot of Resources</p>",
